# DeckVault — TCG Collection Manager

Supported games: Yu-Gi-Oh, Pokemon, Digimon.

Goals: track collection, build decks, track prices, wishlists, market comparison, import/export, statistics, collection value over time.

## Roadmap

**Phase 1:** Auth, Dashboard, Sidebar, Collection, Search, Import CSV, Responsive, Windows launcher (.bat/.exe)

**Phase 2:** Deck Builder, Wishlist, Folders, Bulk Edit, Tags

**Phase 3:** Price Tracking, Graphs, Market Comparison, Trading, Statistics

**Phase 4:** Community, Profiles, Sharing, Trades, Comments, Friends, Notifications
